* **RDAP Triad Action**: Co-chairs will publish a summary of the ad-hoc meeting consensus regarding `draft-ietf-regext-rdap-extensions`, `draft-ietf-regext-rdap-versioning`, and `draft-ietf-regext-rdap-x-media-type` to the mailing list.
* **Mailing List Timer**: A two-week review period will commence upon publication of the ad-hoc summary. If no major objections are raised, `draft-ietf-regext-rdap-extensions` will quickly proceed to WGLC.
* **GitHub Pilot Action**: Jorge Cano will publish the drafted GitHub tool policy document to the mailing list for comment. `draft-ietf-regext-epp-same-entity` will be moved to the IETF REGEXT GitHub organization to initiate the experiment.

